<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.2">
<l>pērāṉaik kuṟuṅkuṭiyem perumāṉai tirutaṇkāl</l>
<l>ūrāṉaik karampaṉū ruttamaṉai muttilaṅku</l>
<l>kārārttiṇ kaṭalēḻum malaiyēḻiv vulakēḻuṇ</l>
<l>ṭārāteṉ ṟiruntāṉaik kaṇṭatuteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] beholding of the one of Pēr, our lord of Kuṟunkuṭi,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one whose city is Tirutaṇkāl,</l>
<l>Supreme of Karampaṉūr, the one who remains never sated,</l>
<l rend="indent">[even] having consumed</l>
<l>The seven rain-filled, powerful seas where pearls glitter,</l>
<l>The seven mountains, and these seven worlds, was in Araṅkam of the South.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
